    <section class="section" id="service-plan"><div class="routine shell"><div class="routine-copy reveal"><div class="kicker">Before the oven clean</div><h2>Cool, empty and ready for attention.</h2><p>Oven Cleaning is a focused service rather than a regular home-cleaning schedule. Preparing the appliance correctly gives the cleaner safe access to the cavity, racks, trays and accessible door glass.</p><div class="frequencies"><div class="frequency"><strong>Switch off</strong><span>Do not use the oven before the appointment.</span></div><div class="frequency"><strong>Let it cool</strong><span>The appliance must be completely cold.</span></div><div class="frequency"><strong>Empty it</strong><span>Remove cookware, foil and personal trays.</span></div><div class="frequency"><strong>Share details</strong><span>Mention unusual models or heavy buildup.</span></div></div><a class="button blue" href="/booking">Book oven cleaning <i><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M4 10h11M11 6l4 4-4 4"></path></svg></i></a></div><div class="routine-visual reveal">__ASTRO_IMAGE_2__<div class="routine-quote"><p>Cool appliance. Clear access. Better process.</p><span>Professional oven care</span></div></div></div></section>

    <section class="section soft" id="compare"><div class="shell"><div class="section-head reveal"><div><div class="kicker">Realistic oven results</div><h2>Built-up grease can be cleaned; damage cannot.</h2></div><p>The service targets accessible residue while protecting the appliance and recognising marks caused by age, wear or damaged coatings.</p></div><div class="compare-grid reveal"><article class="clean-option"><span class="option-label">Cleaning scope</span><h3>Accessible grease, racks, trays and glass.</h3><p>The cleaner works on the surfaces and removable components included in the agreed service.</p><ul><li>Accessible internal cavity</li><li>Removable racks and included trays</li><li>Accessible interior door glass</li><li>Handle and exterior final wipe</li></ul></article><article class="clean-option"><span class="option-label">Service limits</span><h3>Permanent marks and repairs sit outside cleaning.</h3><p>Some discolouration remains when coatings, seals or enclosed components are worn or damaged.</p><ul><li>No dismantling sealed door glass</li><li>No appliance repairs or replacement parts</li><li>No guarantee on permanent staining</li><li>Unsafe appliances cannot be cleaned</li></ul><a class="text-link" href="/contact">Ask about your oven <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M4 10h11M11 6l4 4-4 4"></path></svg></a></article></div></div></section>

    <section class="section" id="how"><div class="shell"><div class="section-head reveal"><div><div class="kicker">How it works</div><h2>Book Oven Cleaning in four clear steps.</h2></div><p>Share the appliance details and leave it cool, empty and safe to access.</p></div><div class="process-grid reveal"><article class="process-step"><div class="process-num">Book</div><h3>Add the oven service</h3><p>Book it alone or alongside a suitable home clean.</p></article><article class="process-step"><div class="process-num">Confirm</div><h3>Share appliance details</h3><p>Mention unusual size, features or very heavy buildup.</p></article><article class="process-step"><div class="process-num">Clean</div><h3>Cool and empty it</h3><p>Remove cookware and do not use the oven before arrival.</p></article><article class="process-step"><div class="process-num">Check</div><h3>Review aftercare</h3><p>Wait until surfaces are dry and follow the cleaner instructions.</p></article></div></div></section>

    <section class="section support"><div class="support-panel shell reveal"><div class="support-copy"><span class="whatsapp"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M20 11.5a8 8 0 0 1-11.8 7L4 20l1.5-4A8 8 0 1 1 20 11.5Z"></path><path d="M8.5 9.5c1 2.2 2.1 3.3 4.3 4.3"></path></svg></span><div><h3>Unsure what your home needs?</h3><p>Send us a quick WhatsApp message with the home size, condition and preferred date.</p></div></div><a class="button blue" href="/contact#whatsapp">Ask on WhatsApp <i><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M4 10h11M11 6l4 4-4 4"></path></svg></i></a></div></section>

    <section class="section faq" id="faqs"><div class="faq-layout shell"><div class="faq-intro reveal"><div class="kicker">Oven Cleaning FAQs</div><h2>Oven Cleaning questions, answered.</h2><p>The practical answers that help make the first visit simple.</p><a class="text-link" href="/faqs">Explore all FAQs <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"><path d="M4 10h11M11 6l4 4-4 4"></path></svg></a></div><div class="faq-list reveal">
      <article class="faq-item open"><h3><button type="button" class="faq-question" aria-expanded="true">How much does Oven Cleaning cost?<span class="faq-plus"></span></button></h3><div class="answer"><div><p>$65 for a standard oven. Discuss larger or unusual appliances before booking.</p></div></div></article><article class="faq-item"><h3><button type="button" class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">How long does it take?<span class="faq-plus"></span></button></h3><div class="answer"><div><p>Most standard ovens take approximately 45 minutes to one hour.</p></div></div></article><article class="faq-item"><h3><button type="button" class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">Is it included in Standard Cleaning?<span class="faq-plus"></span></button></h3><div class="answer"><div><p>No. Standard Cleaning covers the exterior only. Dedicated interior cleaning is an add-on.</p></div></div></article><article class="faq-item"><h3><button type="button" class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">How should I prepare the oven?<span class="faq-plus"></span></button></h3><div class="answer"><div><p>Switch it off, let it cool completely and remove cookware, foil and personal trays.</p></div></div></article><article class="faq-item"><h3><button type="button" class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">Can every permanent mark be removed?<span class="faq-plus"></span></button></h3><div class="answer"><div><p>No. Permanent discolouration, damaged coatings and inaccessible sealed areas may remain.</p></div></div></article><article class="faq-item"><h3><button type="button" class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">Can I combine it with another service?<span class="faq-plus"></span></button></h3><div class="answer"><div><p>Yes. It can be paired with Standard, Deep or Move-In Cleaning and is already included in the current End of Lease scope.</p></div></div></article>
      </div></div></section>

